title: Desperate Housewives || 9 To 5
author: Real Scorsese
comment: I loved this show in high school. These women are soooo amazing. I literally wrote an entire blog post about how these types of characters inspired me. Andrew was my first example of gays on tv and while admittedly not the best representation the issues that he and Bree worked through on screen translated so hard to me.
Funny ! Le passage des baffes, les péripéties des personnages de la serie est la zik (bon choix) apportent une touche bien sympathoche :)
Good job bro, I've seen this show on T.V when I was young and I still remember how good it was! Very nice to see a video for Desperate Housewives and especially by you, just amazing! :D
